                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="vertical-align:top;">
                        <td style="padding-top:20px;padding-right:30px;"> 
                            <ul>
                                   <b>Appointment Date and Time: </b><apex:outputText value="{0,date,long}">
<apex:param value="{!relatedTo.Appointment_Date__c}" />
</apex:outputText> {!relatedTo.Appointment_Time__c}<br/>

                                    <b>Location:</b> Online.<br/>
                              <br/>
                                                                                                                                    
                                <p><b>Instructions:</b></p>
                                
                                    At the time of your appointment, simply open this link:{!relatedTo.Account.Owner.Division}<br/>
                                    
                                    <br/>
                                    Your Energy Consultant’s presentation will appear on your screen. 
                                    You will receive a call from your Energy Consultant at this time to go over the presentation. 
                                    <br/>

                                    <b>You will be meeting with {!relatedTo.Account.Owner.Name}</b><br/> 
                                     
                                    <b>Phone:</b> {!relatedTo.Account.Owner.Phone}<br/> 
                                     
                                    <b>Email:</b> {!relatedTo.Account.Owner.email} <br/><br/>
                                    
                               
                                  <!--  <b>Click <apex:outputLink value="http://sunpower.force.com/DesignSignOff/apex/MeetYourConsultant?id={!relatedTo.Account.OwnerId}" id="eventlink"> here</apex:outputLink> to learn more about your Energy Consultant. </b>           
<br/><br/><br/> -->
                               
                            </ul>
                               
                        </td>
